an> 標題：預備葬埋屍體（body preparation）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">裹屍布、壽衣：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.5.3.7 麻、亞麻、細麻布 (linen)&lt;REALIA:1.5.3.7&gt;</a> 。</h2>\n</div>",
